   <text id="WB36">
        <metadata>
            <title>"Why Towhee Has Red Eyes"</title>
            <author>Nettie <alph>Reuben</alph></author>
            <date>1957</date>
            <publication>William Bright, <em>The Karok Language</em> (1957), pp. 238-239
</publication>
        </metadata>
        <data>
            <paragraph>
                <s>
                    <kar>
		<w gl="Towhee"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="693">asmáax</m></w>
		<w gl="has red eyes"><m id="7239">yúp</m><m id="78">'aaxkunish</m></w>. </kar>
<eng>Towhee has red eyes.</eng>
</s>
<s>
<kar>
<w gl="arrowhead"><m id="5203">saak</m></w>
<w gl="were attaching arrowheads"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="5785">táxraat</m><m id="6648">vunaa</m></w>.
</kar>
<eng>They were attaching arrowheads.</eng>
</s>
<s>
<kar>
<w gl="so"><m id="6570">víri</m><m id="6377">va</m></w>
<w><m id="3670">káan</m></w>
<w gl="he was watching"><m id="6175">ú</m><m id="2585">muustih</m></w>.</kar>
<eng>He was watching there.</eng>
</s>
<s>
<kar>
<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
<w gl="when"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
<w gl="they finished"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="4903">píkyaar</m></w>
<w gl="attaching arrowheads"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="5785">táxraa</m><m id="6035">ti</m></w>
<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
<w gl="Towhee"><m id="693">asmáax</m></w>
<w><m id="6042">tîi</m></w>
<w gl="me pick up"><m id="3735">kan</m><m id="1468">'ífik</m><m id="1419">i</m></w>
<w gl="the scraps"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="5785">taxrat</m><m id="1244">êep</m></w>.</kar>
<eng>And when they finished attaching arrowheads, then Towhee thought, "Let me pick up the scraps".</eng>
</s>
<s>
<kar>
<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
<w gl="he attached arrowheads"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="5785">táxraa</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>.</kar>
<eng>Then he attached arrowheads.</eng>
</s>
<s>
<kar>
<w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>
<w><m id="6307">uum</m></w>
<w gl="was"><m id="5506">t</m><m id="6175">óo</m></w>
<w><m id="2400">mchaaxripaa</m></w>.</kar>
<eng>The heat was coming out (of the fire).</eng>
</s>
<s>
<kar>
<w gl="when he looked at"><m id="4408">p</m><m id="6175">óo</m><m id="2570">muus</m><m id="6035">ti</m></w>
<w gl="his arrowhead-attaching"><m id="4408">p</m><m id="6175">oo</m><m id="5785">táxraa</m><m id="6035">ti</m></w>
<w gl="into the fire"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="16">'áak</m></w>
<w gl="he looked"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="5506">t</m><m id="3858">kírih</m></w>.</kar>
<eng>When he looked at his arrowhead-attaching, he looked into the fire.</eng>
</s>
<s>
<kar>
<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
<w><m id="3971">kumá'ii</m></w>
<w gl="his eyes"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="4260">mú</m><m id="7239">yuup</m></w>
<w><m id="78">aaxkúnish</m></w>
<w gl="from the heat that came out"><m id="4408">p</m><m id="6175">oo</m><m id="2407">mchaaxrípaa</m><m id="1369">nik</m></w>.</kar>
<eng>So for that reason his eyes are red from the heat that came out.</eng>
</s>
</paragraph>
</data>
